data.description: Check Out this Cute & Quaint 3 Bedroom 2 Bath Two Story Home in Valley View School District located in Farmersville with many Walkable Amenities.  Property Features a 1st Floor Primary Bedroom with Full Bathroom & 2 Bedrooms 1 Bathroom on Second Floor.  Newer Roof Windows & Many Updates Throughout.  Fenced Back Yard, 2 Car Detached Garage, Appliances Stay & More!  Listing is located in a USDA-RD Eligible Area for up to 100% Zero Down Loan!
